summary: Small player house built into the side of a waterfall.
descriptionHtml:
[b]==== Water-fall Shack ==== [/b]

This mod adds a small player home built into the side of a waterfall in the Rift. This is good for starting characters or people who want a place with a view. The door to the shack is locked by the previous owner. Read the note in the stachel to start on the right direction. 

[b]==== Features ==== [/b]

+Small Player home on the side of a waterfall 
+Amazing views 
+Player owned bed and containers for your treasure 
+Tanning Rack and Blacksmiths Anvil 
+Enchanting Table and free soul gem 
+Separate Cooking area 
+DIVING BOARD!!! 
+Fishing dock with fish rack 

If you need help to find the key check the last 2 images 

Please rate up this mod if you enjoy it and feedback is welcome.

Available on the Steam Workshop: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=329956644
